Class CrimeAnalysisServiceImlp

  • java.lang.Object
    • dao.ICrimeAnalysisService
      • dao.CrimeAnalysisServiceImlp

  • public class CrimeAnalysisServiceImlp
extends ICrimeAnalysisService
    The CrimeAnalysisServiceImlp class provides implementations for various functionalities related to crime analysis. It extends the abstract class ICrimeAnalysisService and implements its abstract methods. This class interacts with the database to perform CRUD operations on incidents and cases.
